CustomField.description: If set, this overrides the Global Assignment Quota for this Assignment Group. Specifies the maximum number of records allowed to be assigned to this user in the Quota Period across all Assignment Groups for the specified object type
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If set, this overrides the Global Assignment Quota for this Assignment Group. Specifies the maximum number of records allowed to be assigned to this user in the Quota Period across all Assignment Groups for the specified object type
CustomField.label: Global Assignment Quota
